<br>
That being said I believe strongly that 2 groups can do all of Fear except the mini-bosses. Heres the breakdown -<br>
<br>
2 Identical groups:<br>
1 55+ Bard<br>
1 55+ Enchanter<br>
1 56+ Cleric<br>
3 56+ Wizards <br>
<br>
Invis up and run to the ledge, letting the bards go first, with AE fear song goin full tilt (if you have 2 60 bards let em hit DA song as soon as they hit the ground then run as a group to the ledge, if not, stick to this)<br>
<br>
You must remember to stand as near as possible to on top of each other...<br>
<br>
When mobs arrive Bards twist AE slow/snare Cantana of Replenishment and a debuff song (if possible). i.e. both do Cantana one does ae slow/snare, other does resist debuff.<br>
<br>
Chanters just chain stun for all they are worth. You may want one to AE tash as second cast, while one just stuns.<br>
<br>
6 Wizards chain nuking Jylls should waste any roamers you get.<br>
<br>
If you do not seem to have much of a train, send one bard out with selos to round up some more. He can sing AE slow to help create a decent train (remember if the mobs are within melee range only 3 will stick to a single toon, others will forget you).<br>
<br>
Once dead, med up (c2 + cantana = fast med) and send the bard for more.<br>
<br>
Done properly I think Fear lasts about 1 hr before you hit minis. Temple will require the Clerics to pull, and you should all move over close so DA doesnt wear off, also have SoW potions or jboots for your clerics.<br>
<br>
At this point you may allow those useless Melees to come in so you can drop the mini-bosses :-)<br>
<br>
Malagis(x) Windrider<br>
AE Prophet of Gnomallah<br>
The Hand<br>
Xev <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uzzappbrell.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zzapp Brell</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/29/01 1:08:08 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: AE PoF Idea</span><hr size=1> We've done it on Brell with around 18-22 people, and it was a blast. <br>
<br>
Need at least 5 wizards 56+.<br>
Need at least 3-4 chanters (around 55+)<br>
<br>
Also need single pull elements in the raid.  When that HUGE fun train is all dead, almost all your wizards are OOM.  thats when you need tanks to block for you and keep those baddies off the medding casters.<br>
<br>
We cleared fear in about 2 hours once the pulls got started, and I'm sure that it was our personal record for clearing fear.  <br>
<br>
<br>
Zzapp &lt;Skyre Draneth&gt; of Brell<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uelaurieldragonstorm.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Elauriel Dragonstorm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/30/01 10:00:26 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: AE PoF Idea</span><hr size=1> We had two level 60 enchanters, 2 55+ wizards,  a handful of druids and mages for additional AoE support, plus a few clerics, tanks etc.  I personally had no problems with resist in Fear, and I don't believe the enchanters did either.<br>
<br>
The main issue I found was that the puller would bring a few mobs in, but they seemed to have a hard time getting them to us all wrapped into a ball for easier AoE.<br>
<br>
I think having at least one more wizard and one more enchanter would have made it much smoother and less mana intensive. <p><img src ="http://www.guildmagic.com/pics/32282.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm21.showMessage?topicID=96.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm21.showMessage?topicID=90.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm21.emailToFriend?topicID=95.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm21.threadControl?topicID=95.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm21.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=95.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm21.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=95.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm3">Trade Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm4">Rant Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm8">Mob Dropped Spells<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm10">Class Balance & Class Bugs<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm22">Out of Mana<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm27">PVP Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm28">The Library<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm25">Share Your Mana<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm18">Admin<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm19">Soloing<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm20">AE Kiting<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm21">AE Grouping<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm2">General Quests<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm5">Staff of the Four - Epic Quest<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm26">Circlet of the Falinkan<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm23">Duties for the Crown<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm31">Fusibility Research<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm15">Hsagra's Wrath<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm12">Kael Drakkal Armor<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm14">Skyshrine Armor<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm7">Frostbeards Armor<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm9">Phenocryst's Focus<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm17">Plane of Sky<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm16">Porlos' Fury<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm13">Rough Silver Chain<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm24">Staff of the Wheel - Ice Comet<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm11">Velium Chill of Al'Kabor<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm6">Tome of Ages Quest<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm29">Translocational Suppressions<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm30">Veeshan's Peak Key</select></td><td><input type=submit value="Go" class=inputbutton></td></tr></table></form></td></tr></table><br><font color=#ffffff>- </font><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation>Graffë's Wizard Discussion</a><font color=#ffffff> - </font><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilation